{"tid":1881282,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"(日本奧運城市)  東京一日新增8宗「武漢肺炎」確診","createTime":"2020-02-15T12:27:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-17T05:59:41.000Z","uid":134071,"like":15,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"0dc02207a546a64cfe1c4ebd92f47d96160b44de","tid":1881282,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T12:27:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/life/20200215/664UQBDORQIZROIEDKNSXEFXOI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Flife%2F20200215%2F664UQBDORQIZROIEDKNSXEFXOI%2F&d=uD1rvIJwXfBqs1i1iclFx8TiFwqRwBg1VWT7Je45URE%3D&h=08c82662\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Flife%2F20200215%2F664UQBDORQIZROIEDKNSXEFXOI%2F&h=7ad83a97\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/life/20200215/664UQBDORQIZROIEDKNSXEFXOI/</a><br />\n<br />\n【武漢肺炎分布圖】東京失控！司機餐會10人確診、日本激增至338例 《蘋果》速報掌握全球<br />\n34分鐘<br />\n<br />\n<strong>日本厚生勞動省今下午宣布</strong>，鑽石公主號新增67例，其中38人無症狀，全船確診者累計已285例；<strong>東京新增8例</strong>，這8人當中有7人與前天確診的東京計程車司機有關；今晚名古屋再增1人確診，是昨天名古屋確診男子的妻子。埃及周五（14日，台灣今凌晨）「淪陷」，該國首見武漢肺炎確診病例，這也是非洲的首例。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://appledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com/resizer/x2oQF9zNefd74TX_vSgc7EBUn-8=/760x535/arc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com/ap-ne-1-prod/public/ZAGW7JBZPJ5VK2TVO3MHO4YT7A.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fappledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com%2Fresizer%2Fx2oQF9zNefd74TX_vSgc7EBUn-8%3D%2F760x535%2Farc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fap-ne-1-prod%2Fpublic%2FZAGW7JBZPJ5VK2TVO3MHO4YT7A.jpg&h=90bf0eb7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ce82f0bdc086af57415a3fd232dcf6582d8c783d","tid":1881282,"uid":134071,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T12:28:15.000Z","msg":"(binc)  日本政府不斷打壓AV界 , 主要為了2020年東京奧運<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/187